OL,2,W+.!/*% *%*%/*%,.! /.!/*%,.!S,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 02 MAY
OL,4,CTELETEXT
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1983FCeefax In-Vision (later known as
OL,7,FPages from Ceefax) officially replaces
OL,8,FTest Card F as a daytime interval
OL,9,Ffiller on BBC One and BBC Two.
OL,10,
OL,11,FCeefax pages had been appearing in
OL,12,Fdaytime slots since March 1980 but Test
OL,13,FCard F continued to fill most of the
OL,14,Fgaps in the daytime programme schedule.
OL,15,
OL,16,FOn 2nd May 1983, the first Ceefax
OL,17,FIn-Vision slot was: BBC Two 11.25am -
OL,18,F2.20pm. As this was a Bank Holiday, BBC
OL,19,FOne had a full daytime schedule.
OL,20,
OL,21,FThe new, regular Ceefax In-Vision
OL,22,Fservice on BBC One (excluding Ceefax
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
